<div class="artwork-content">

        <div id="artwork-image">
            <a href="..\/images\/187432_4228729.jpg" class="enlargement-link enlargement-link-27310"><img src="images/187432_4228731.jpg" alt="The Holy Family with Saints Elizabeth and John the Baptist" title="Peter Paul Rubens
